data.description: Step into the timeless charm of this meticulously restored 1932 gem! This captivating home is a true testament to history, artfully preserved and thoughtfully remodeled to accentuate its original features. Experience the allure of yesteryear as you enter this enchanting residence, where every corner tells a story of its own. From the elegant coffered ceilings, to the exquisite floors and fireplaces, no detail has been overlooked. The remodeled interior seamlessly blends the best of both worlds - vintage allure and modern comfort. Living and dining areas have tall ceilings, the front bedroom could double as an office or sun room with ample natural light from the picture windows. The well-appointed kitchen and upgraded bathroom adds a touch of luxury, ensuring a harmonious blend of old-world charm and modern functionality. Outside, the home sits on a generous corner lot. The curb appeal is simply captivating, beckoning you to explore the historic charm that lies within. You don't want to miss this one, call today for more information!
